      • setLogFormat

        public static void setLogFormat(java.lang.String logFormat)
        Set the format of all logged messages
        Parameters:
        logFormat - The format to use
        %c will be replaced with the location it was called from
        %t will be replaced with the time since init was called
        %T will be replaced with the thread it is called from
        %l will be replaced with the log level
        %m will be replaced with the message
        the default is [%t][%c][%T] %m\n
